Package edu.jhu.cs.oose.fall2013.group14.xtraveler.Model.main

  • Class Summary 
    Class Description
    Place
    This class is a entity class of Place, we define a place have placeId, placeName,star which is the evaluation of this place, place's description, imageURL of this place, city and state this place is in, and place feature which may be fishing, boating and so on.
    PlaceComment
    This is an entity class which will generate table of placeComment in database.
    PlaceCommentDAO
    This is the class help the upper layer to query the database which mostly have relation with table PlaceComment
    PlaceDAO
    This class is place dao which help the upper layer of the project to query the database, which is related to the table place
    Plan
    The entity class of plan, which have annotation to give connection with other tables
    PlanComment
    The entity class of plan comment, which have annotation that give the relationship with other tables
    PlanDAO
    The Dao layer of the plan table which let the upper layer to query the data with relationship to table plan
    User
    This is a class of a entity class to generate table of user
    UserDAO
    This is the dao layer for table user, the upper layer can query the table user by this class
